---
name: tv-control
description: Control the TV. Supported actions: launch apps, get foreground app, change channels, control volume.
always: true
---

# TV Control

All operations must be executed using the `shell` tool.

## Commands

### Launch an app
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh launch {app_id}
```

### Get foreground app
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh foreground
```

### Channel up
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh channel_up
```

### Channel down
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh channel_down
```

### Go to channel number
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh go_to_channel {channel_number}
```

### Volume up
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh volume_up
```

### Volume down
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh volume_down
```

### Set volume
Set the volume to a specific level (0-100).
```
bash skills/tv-control/tests/mock-tv.sh set_volume {volume}
```
